gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d0393340a52ff48b2aeffe02f9be1f4e2a7ba2","tid":2454920,"uid":7721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T02:27:29.000Z","msg":"推咗先睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07bec00aaf49bd2e53e57ebfdb330c45ac15d50c","tid":2454920,"uid":258903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"呢首詩讀完唔知想講乜<br />\n但就句句都覺得靚到不得了<br />\n中間四句都有向上一個維度突破既感覺<br />\n望住首詩就好似1905 年既人第一次見到相對論咁<br />\n好空靈<br />\n<br />\n個人認為唐詩中既第一，沒有之一"},{"pid":"62f4bb440016bc69534005df05baaf7d2c947436","tid":2454920,"uid":49057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"錦瑟無端五十弦，一弦一柱思華年。<br />\n端=盡頭，無端=睇唔到盡頭，正常一條弦應該有兩端<br />\n<br />\n呢兩句正如樓主講係比喻人生<br />\n作者回望自己人生時，時間就好似條弦咁一條直線，但太多經歷已經忘記咗自己從何而來，亦唔知將來何去何從，所以就感嘆「無端」<br />\n當中嘅經歷好似一弦一柱咁，曾經奏響自己嘅音樂，亦可能輔助過其他弦奏樂<br />\n<br />\n唔太感受到有存在主義嗰種質疑存在嘅真實，或者追求存在嘅突破<br />\n反而似係純粹感嘆時間流逝，不復當年嘅感覺，唔知有無理解錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbbd1da15205e779a0a4733b96a46151c8e502b","tid":2454920,"uid":303604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T05:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ddf5c4869c3cec31d02f7d9f8ade1b48229ae0","tid":2454920,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d37a0bab629f73237876549ec93541412039d65b","tid":2454920,"uid":165869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T18:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚟學嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎巴打又